"archive. Unlike the :meth:`ZipFile.extract` and "
":meth:`ZipFile.extractall` methods, it is the caller's responsibility to "
"validate or sanitize filenames to prevent path traversal vulnerabilities "
"(e.g., filenames containing \"..\" or absolute paths). When handling "
"untrusted archives, consider resolving filenames using "
":func:`os.path.abspath` and checking against the target directory with "
":func:`os.path.commonpath`."
